  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_e60f68915a9279128cc1f8ce40e63efa">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>The Beta chapter of Theta Delta Chi fraternity was established at Cornell University on January 11, 1870.</p>  </bioghist>
